title: Tig Notaro / C-Diff
description: Dr. Wali investigates Sean's tale of his ruptured small intestine. Our friend Tig Notaro (Army of the Dead, One Mississippi) joins us to talk about C-Diff. The team also learns that the heart controls everything!
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
